HEADWORD: Unhouseled
<hw>Un*hou"seled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not having
received the sacrament.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>unhouselled</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To die like the houseless dog on yonder common, unshriven and
<qex>unhouseled</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhuman</ent>⟦br⟧
